	* You need to add the following directory to your CLASSPATH
	  environment.

		${PREFIX}/share/jde/java/lib

	* You might need to increase process heap / stack memory resource
	  limits.

	  	For Bourne shells:
			% ulimit -d unlimited
			% ulimit -s unlimited

	  	For C shells:
			% unlimit datasize
			% unlimit stacksize

	  See sh(1) / csh(1) manual pages for more details.

===========================================================================
